                      </para>
                    </label-para>
                    <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                      <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">ii</label>
                      <para>
                        <text>taking into account international norms, conventions, declarations, covenants, and treaties already supported, signed, or ratified by the New Zealand Government; and</text>
